1
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:08,540
=Fireworks=

2
00:00:08,540 --> 00:00:10,860
=Episode 23=

3
00:00:12,560 --> 00:00:15,240
This is... a bug?

4
00:00:32,039 --> 00:00:33,320
It's my mom.

5
00:00:35,719 --> 00:00:36,759
It's my mom...

6
00:00:38,039 --> 00:00:39,280
It really is my mom.

7
00:00:39,799 --> 00:00:42,479
I knew I didn't mishear
that day at the hospital.

8
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:44,719
It really was her voice.

9
00:00:46,719 --> 00:00:47,799
It really is my mom.

10
00:00:51,799 --> 00:00:53,799
Why did Jiang Xiao lock her up?

11
00:00:55,759 --> 00:00:57,200
Why did she get locked up?

12
00:00:57,560 --> 00:01:00,520
That day, when you heard
the sound of a dolphin at my house,

13
00:01:01,359 --> 00:01:03,719
I paid special attention
to the situation at home.

14
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:06,040
I noticed a maid

15
00:01:06,719 --> 00:01:08,599
always sneaking in and out
of the same place.

16
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:13,719
So I figured your mom must be there.

17
00:01:15,959 --> 00:01:17,599
But why are they

18
00:01:17,959 --> 00:01:19,760
hiding my mom?

19
00:01:21,519 --> 00:01:22,319
I think

20
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:25,200
your mom is probably Jiang Xiao's

21
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:27,079
trump card to control you.

22
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:28,560
She...

23
00:01:29,439 --> 00:01:30,239
I...

24
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:34,799
Don't worry.

25
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:36,799
As long as we rescue her,

26
00:01:37,319 --> 00:01:39,359
Jiang Xiao won't have
any cards left to play.

27
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:42,200
But...

28
00:01:44,079 --> 00:01:47,799
we still need a way
to completely bring down Jiang Xiao.

29
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:52,239
Have you come up
with a way to deal with him?

30
00:01:56,599 --> 00:01:57,519
All these years,

31
00:01:58,120 --> 00:02:00,280
I've been investigating
his companies overseas.

32
00:02:01,319 --> 00:02:03,640
I found out he's been involved
with foreign gangs.

33
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:06,760
But he's been too careful,

34
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:08,599
leaving no evidence behind.

35
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:11,120
But even if we rescue my mom

36
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:12,719
and save Qiao Group,

37
00:02:13,319 --> 00:02:15,000
your brother is still in their hands.

38
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:31,919
My brother...

39
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:38,560
He might already be dead.

40
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:42,919
All these years,

41
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:48,120
I've had Wen Li
helping me search for him.

42
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:53,199
But once he landed overseas,
he just vanished.

43
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,439
I've reached out to friends abroad,

44
00:02:57,439 --> 00:02:58,639
asking them to help.

45
00:03:00,919 --> 00:03:02,080
But after all these years...

46
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,639
there's still no news.

47
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,319
Zechen.

48
00:03:23,599 --> 00:03:24,400
To keep me

49
00:03:26,919 --> 00:03:29,719
under his thumb, Jiang Xiao lied to me,

50
00:03:31,479 --> 00:03:33,000
saying Zemu is still alive.

51
00:03:50,919 --> 00:03:54,000
Don't worry. Zemu's definitely safe.

52
00:03:54,639 --> 00:03:55,759
Okay?

53
00:04:02,159 --> 00:04:03,039
You're right.

54
00:04:04,039 --> 00:04:05,360
We need to take the initiative.

55
00:04:06,199 --> 00:04:08,319
Have Jiang Xiao put on a show with us

56
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:10,240
and let him slip up himself.

57
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:11,960
What do you want to do?

58
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:15,400
I want to find the evidence of him
teaming up with foreign gangs

59
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,720
to suppress competitors

60
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:18,800
and disrupt the market order.

61
00:04:19,839 --> 00:04:21,519
With how cautious he is,

62
00:04:22,079 --> 00:04:23,199
he'll probably

63
00:04:23,879 --> 00:04:25,360
catch us in the act.

64
00:04:26,319 --> 00:04:27,759
That's exactly what we want.

65
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:28,720
What?

66
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,360
You'll try to win him over first,

67
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,720
then I'll go find you

68
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:34,600
and pretend to fall into his trap.

69
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:39,199
I'll hand him the evidence
with the Trojan virus

70
00:04:39,879 --> 00:04:41,480
and let him destroy himself.

71
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:43,680
No, that's too dangerous.

72
00:04:43,839 --> 00:04:45,040
Jiang Xiao is ruthless.

73
00:04:46,519 --> 00:04:49,319
We'll use a firewall to block his view.

74
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:53,279
Don't worry. I'll definitely escape.

75
00:04:53,439 --> 00:04:54,240
No.

76
00:04:55,439 --> 00:04:56,920
I can't let you take the risk.

77
00:04:58,879 --> 00:05:00,120
Trust me.

78
00:05:00,199 --> 00:05:01,519
As long as we work together,

79
00:05:01,519 --> 00:05:02,839
I'll be safe for sure.

80
00:05:05,639 --> 00:05:07,959
How about we set a code phrase?

81
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:10,560
What code phrase?

82
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:16,000
If I tell you I hate you,

83
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:18,519
that means I've safely escaped.

84
00:05:24,879 --> 00:05:28,639
If we want Jiang Xiao
to completely show his cards,

85
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:32,639
we need someone else's help.

86
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:33,959
Who?

87
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,040
What?

88
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:39,839
You want me and Qiao Nian
to act in front of Jiang Xiao?

89
00:05:39,959 --> 00:05:40,759
Yes.

90
00:05:41,279 --> 00:05:42,120
What should we do?

91
00:05:42,260 --> 00:05:43,160
Pretend to get married.

92
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:46,680
Seriously?

93
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:49,560
I'll use the chance to make it real.

94
00:05:49,839 --> 00:05:51,160
Can you calm down?

95
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:52,330
You spit all over my clothes.

96
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:53,800
Want me to catch it with a bowl?

97
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:56,560
Jiang Xiao's goal
is to take over Qiao Group.

98
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,480
Now that Qiao Wenjun's gone,

99
00:06:00,519 --> 00:06:03,480
his next target should be Qiao Nian.

100
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:08,920
There was a crisis
in the company before.

101
00:06:08,930 --> 00:06:09,959
Jiang Xiao took the chance

102
00:06:09,959 --> 00:06:12,160
to sign a betting contract
with Qiao Wenjun.

103
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:14,399
Though it saved the company at the time,

104
00:06:14,399 --> 00:06:16,000
it also created a lot of hidden risks.

105
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:18,839
If the company faces any negative news

106
00:06:18,879 --> 00:06:20,240
or the stock price drops,

107
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:22,439
we'll have to pay him five billion.

108
00:06:22,959 --> 00:06:25,720
And this contract is fully legal

109
00:06:26,319 --> 00:06:27,199
and bulletproof.

110
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:29,720
I can pay that five billion

111
00:06:29,879 --> 00:06:30,680
for Qiao Nian.

112
00:06:31,079 --> 00:06:33,319
But what does this
have to do with marriage?

113
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:36,160
As long as Song Group
becomes Qiao Group's support,

114
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:38,120
Jiang Xiao's plan will fail.

115
00:06:38,959 --> 00:06:42,040
But he'll definitely try
to use my mom to his advantage.

116
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:45,000
So, we need to use a wedding

117
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:46,720
to create an alibi for Qiao Nian.

118
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:49,000
We'll need Wen Li
to work with us on this.

119
00:06:49,439 --> 00:06:50,279
No problem.

120
00:06:50,959 --> 00:06:53,319
To buy Qiao Nian enough time
to save her mother,

121
00:06:54,399 --> 00:06:56,839
I've already handed
her list of financial backers

122
00:06:56,839 --> 00:06:57,839
over to Jiang Xiao.

123
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:02,920
This way,
Qiao Nian's fundraising should fail.

124
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:05,079
By then, Jiang Xiao will think

125
00:07:05,079 --> 00:07:06,839
there's a rift between me and Qiao Nian.

126
00:07:07,759 --> 00:07:10,240
Then, it's up to all of you.

127
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,079
So when's the wedding?

128
00:07:12,759 --> 00:07:13,600
Three days from now.

129
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:20,879
You have to stay safe.

130
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:22,960
I'll leave an exit open for you.

131
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:33,720
Jiang Zechen!

132
00:07:34,199 --> 00:07:35,879
I hate you!

133
00:07:35,879 --> 00:07:37,279
- Stop!
- Don't run!

134
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:47,040
My dear son and daughter-in-law,

135
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:50,360
where do you think you're running to?

136
00:07:50,439 --> 00:07:51,240
Jiang Xiao.

137
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:53,760
Evidence of your crimes
is all over the internet.

138
00:07:54,959 --> 00:07:58,040
Did Xie Yunyi copy my phone?

139
00:07:58,480 --> 00:07:59,639
So what if she did?

140
00:08:00,399 --> 00:08:01,959
You should turn back now.

141
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:08,000
You think you can
bring me down like this?

142
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:11,920
Don't forget.
Xie Yunyi is still in my hands.

143
00:08:12,959 --> 00:08:14,680
No, no, no.

144
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,480
Those losers you hired?

145
00:08:16,639 --> 00:08:18,040
I took them out in seconds.

146
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:31,360
Impressive.

147
00:08:42,519 --> 00:08:44,919
Mr. Jiang,
we'll bring her to you in a bit.

148
00:08:46,559 --> 00:08:47,480
How could this be?

149
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:57,240
Well, well. A brilliant double-play.

150
00:08:58,600 --> 00:09:00,039
My dear son.

151
00:09:01,279 --> 00:09:03,519
You've really grown up.

152
00:09:04,679 --> 00:09:06,759
I simply prepared a contingency plan.

153
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:12,360
You think you're the only one
who knows how to prepare?

154
00:09:20,275 --> 00:09:21,350
(Bomb activated)

155
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:22,799
No one moves.

156
00:09:24,039 --> 00:09:26,320
The bomb detonator is in my hands.

157
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,279
Anyone moves,

158
00:09:27,279 --> 00:09:29,039
and I'll blow you all!

159
00:09:34,150 --> 00:09:40,120
♪So many words unsaid,
the deeper we fall, the more we fear♪

160
00:09:40,400 --> 00:09:48,000
♪Fate like a gamble,
locking us inside its game♪

161
00:09:48,050 --> 00:09:51,840
♪Hearts at play, truth and lies,
who could ever know♪

162
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:55,640
♪Where this ends♪

163
00:09:55,640 --> 00:10:02,920
♪I try to walk away,
yet still step into the fire♪

164
00:10:02,920 --> 00:10:07,250
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

165
00:10:07,290 --> 00:10:10,370
♪Love turns into pain♪

166
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:14,560
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

167
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:18,200
♪Yet I still want you close♪

168
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:22,370
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

169
00:10:22,370 --> 00:10:25,680
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

170
00:10:25,680 --> 00:10:30,250
♪When love and hate fade
into the crowd and the ice melts♪

171
00:10:30,250 --> 00:10:36,560
♪Does it mean we could meet again?♪

172
